I may not have finished the first draft for SV book 2 before 2023, but I DID hit 100,000 words and for that I’m ecstatic—no matter how many books i write, that 100k goal is always a rush!

Don’t worry though! I’m on the home run. As soon as I pump through the finale of this story, I can get a move on getting the publishing ball rolling. 

Let’s go, 2023 🔥
I’m so thankful to who I was at 14 💞

Good morning! Can we believe that January is nearly already over😮‍💨 

This time last year I was selling preorders of my debut book Silver Valley, and now in 2023 I’m sooooo close to finishing the first draft of book 2! Isn’t that crazy! Time blinks by like nothing, but I’ve loved every second of it 🫶🏼

Hope you all are having a great year so far!
Filmed this today to hold myself accountable. Another 2 days like today, and the first draft of my next book will be done! I can’t wait for Silver Valley 2! (Title announcement to come) 🪐

Can you believe that I’m DAYS away from finishing book 2 of Silver Valley??

The other day I ordered a bunch more books and also created a code you guys can add to get a 10% discount off all signed Silver Valley books from my website!

SV10 for 10% off 🪐✨🫶🏼

Can’t wait for you all to read book 2!

Soooo I started a thing… 🏃‍♀️

*side note, the Maze won’t end up this tall! I’ll be building the base up with a ground base when I finish this layer 🫶🏼

So excited for this project omg.

I finished writing book 2 of Silver Valley yesterday!!! Screaming!!

It’s currently sitting at 120k words prior to edits, which is 12k more than book 1! Going to bury myself in edits now. I never thought I’d say it, but I’m excited to begin the editing process again!

Title reveal and release date to come—expect it mid this year 🫶🏼

I’m currently working on my manuscript with my BETA readers and have a cover in the works (will do a cover reveal as soon as possible)! And then I can start on EDITING❤️‍🔥

I’m screaming, crying, throwing up, loving the way this book is turning out. So far, the feedback has been better than I could have hoped for, and I cannot wait for book 2 of the Silver Valley trilogy to release later this year ✨

Coming Monday 20th ❤️‍🔥

Welcome back to the Silver Valley trilogy! And set your timers, because a cover reveal & preorders for book 2 is dropping in SIX DAYS🔥✨

Both eBooks (on Amazon) and signed books (inclusive of a preorder goodie) will be available on my website: www.arabellarosier.com

And if that isn’t exciting enough—each day in the lead up I will be sharing tidbits about this book, so keep your eyes peeled every morning!

Let’s go!!
❤️‍🔥 Cover reveal & preorders: 6 days❤️‍🔥

Book 2 of the Silver Valley trilogy, cover reveal and preorders, LIVE Monday 20th ❤️‍🔥

Today is day 5 in the count down for the cover reveal of book 2 in the SV trilogy, and I’m dropping in to share some quotes from the book!

Because we all love a good sneak peek ;)

❤️‍🔥 Cover reveal & preorders: 5 days❤️‍🔥

Book 2 of the Silver Valley trilogy, cover reveal and preorders, LIVE Monday 20th ❤️‍🔥

Today’s reveal is an exciting one! 
Drum roll please!

Book 2 of SV will be a duel POV! Featuring our favourite hacker, Melanie Beckett 🔐

The story starts off as we began in Silver Valley, through the eyes of Savannah Shaw, but as the story progresses, we begin to split into 2—following the POV of both Savannah AND Melanie.

I can’t wait for you all to experience the Valley through Beckett’s eyes!

 ❤️‍🔥Cover reveal & preorders: 4 days❤️‍🔥

Book 2 of the Silver Valley trilogy, cover reveal and preorders, LIVE Monday 20th ❤️‍🔥

Today, I’m going to be sharing with you the abbreviation of the title!

The next book in the series goes by S.K. ✨

Any guesses as to what the title can be?

 ❤️‍🔥Cover reveal & preorders: 3 days❤️‍🔥

Book 2 of the Silver Valley trilogy, cover reveal and preorders, LIVE Monday 20th ❤️‍🔥

Project SK, the second book in the Silver Valley trilogy, explores some darker topics than in book 1. Because of this, I’m announcing a few content warnings for whoever may need it.

CONTENT WARNING:
This story contains minor profanity, violence, and topics that may be sensitive to some readers. For a detailed list, please visit arabellarosier.com/content-warnings

I believe that even the smallest mention in a book may be a trigger to some, which is why I feel the need to mention these warnings. Love you all 🫶🏼

 ❤️‍🔥Cover reveal & preorders: 2 days❤️‍🔥

Book 2 of the Silver Valley trilogy, cover reveal and preorders, LIVE TOMORROW ❤️‍🔥

We are ONE DAY away from the cover and preorders going live for SK!! Are you screaming? I’m screaming.

Today, let’s end this count down with a bang! 
It’s time to announce the blurb!

••••••
It has taken Savannah Shaw 17 years to reach the kingdom in the stars. But does Umbra want her there?

Silver Valley is gone, and from its ashes, a rebellion stirs. 

Savannah Shaw is nothing but a product of people’s dreams, a hope to spark the flame. But her desire to win Umbra is the key to everything. The kingdom is all you could ever want, a world sprawling with beauty and life. In order to obtain her, Savannah must navigate death and sacrifice, love and betrayal, to win Umbra’s hand.

Back home, Melanie Beckett tames the waters. Without an army, the Silver Kingdom is lost. Allies come to their aid, new love rekindles, and old hope dies.

What do you have to lose, in order to win? 
••••••

See you all tomorrow for the reveal!

 ❤️‍🔥Cover reveal & preorders: 1 day❤️‍🔥

WELCOME TO SILVER KINGDOM❤️‍🔥

The second book in the Silver Valley trilogy!🌙✨

This book is my heart. My soul. My everything. I’m so excited to bring Savannah back onto the pages, and back into your hearts. 

JUNE 30, LETS GOOO❤️‍🔥

SILVER KINGDOM. Coming June 30th, 2023 ❤️‍🔥

I’m screaming, crying, clutching my heart—excited and overwhelmed is the biggest understatement of the century.

Preorders for signed copies are now LIVE on my website! Each book comes hand signed, with a FREE preorder goodie (will be sharing details on this later). And eBook preorders are also up on Amazon!
All these links can be found on my page 🌙✨

Stars, the feeling of releasing a book is so MAGICAL. I’m so grateful to be here and so ecstatic to be sharing this world with you again! And if I say anything about this book, let it be this: YOU GUYS ARE GONNA LOVE THIS ONE. 

A massive shoutout to my astonishing cover designer, @gabby_kell, WORDS CANNOT EXPLAIN how amazing you are. I’m in awe over you every time. 

I love you all ❤️‍🔥 
The countdown to June 30th begins!
If you don’t fangirl over your own books, are you even doing it right??🥺✨

If I never doubted myself in 2015, I wouldn’t be where I am in 2023. Follow dem dreams, lovelies 🫶🏼

Silver Kingdom is the second book in the Silver Valley trilogy by Arabella Rosier. 
If you like science fiction and fantasy, as well as a sprinkling of romance, this book is for you! And even if you don’t, there is something for everyone to enjoy from great characters to a beautiful, well developed story line. 

Interested in finding out more? Check out the author’s Instagram (@bookisharabella) or visit her website https://www.arabellarosier.com

FINAL BONUS CHAPTER IS UP ❤️‍🔥

This one is a Lily chapter (AND MAJOR SPOILERS FOR SILVER KINGDOM).

Please, please, please do not read this chapter until you’ve finished Silver Kingdom, book 2 of the Silver Valley trilogy, because not only does it spoil some major plot points, it will also spoil some major end-of-book events.

On that note though, I’m soooo ridiculously excited to share this chapter with you all!! I wanted to include this bonus chapter in the book. Honestly, it's the only bonus chapter I really had to think hard about cutting, because it felt so integral to the story. But ultimately, I cut it because this book did not feel like this characters story. 

Silver Kingdom is a Savannah x Melanie story, and this is a new character that only came into the book 1/3rd of the way through.

I'm so glad to have a means to finally share this snippet with you all though. It really bridges a lot of links towards some questions in the end of the book, so I hope you all enjoy it!

Happy reading 🌲✨🐈
